Co-Authored-By: Cyril Cohen <cohen@crans.org>

additionally:
- derive.v does not Require Reals anymore;
- renaming: UniformNormed -> Topological, Rbar -> ereal, \-inf, \+int -> -oo, +oo;
- generalize extended reals (in a new file ereal.v) to relax types landau.v;
- generalizations: IVT Rdefinitions.R -> realType; various w.r.t.
- numDomainType's;
- Rbar not used in most files anymore,
- no more Require Import Order.Syntax and Order.Def,
- avoid Importing Num.Def (so that some minr became Num.min),
- fix the lemma ball_center (it is now a working Hint)

normedtype.v now uses numDomainType et al. in lieu of AbsRingType and
many definitions have been generalized from Redefinitions.R;
landau.v 43%

matrix_normedModType made canonical;
add the Uniform.ball m = ball norm axiom to uniformNormedZmoduleType,
prod_norm done;
complete the translation from the old to the new structure definitions
but still struggling with the inference of filters;
generalization for normedModType_hausdorff:
global instance declarations

